To add the `disko` package from the `nix-community/disko` repository to your `environment.systemPackages`, you can add the following line to your `configuration.nix` file:

```
environment.systemPackages = with pkgs; [
  (import (builtins.fetchGit {
    url = "https://github.com/nix-community/disko.git";
    rev = "master"; # or use the commit hash you want to use
  }) { }).disko
];
```

